description: Always-on customer health command center. A CSM Lead and Health Analyst track account health scores, usage trends, support tickets, renewal risk, and relationship strength — publishing weekly health refreshes, at-risk alerts, and a live portfolio dashboard. Replaces Gainsight-lite dashboards, Vitally trackers, ChurnZero alerts, and the spreadsheets around them.
